== Refinery Generator

== Description
Generates a new tab in Refinery automatically. All files will be setup and the basic functionality to edit a model in place.

You will want to pass in the name of the model this tab is for. Use the singular name.

The first attribute should always be the one which is the title or name of the model.

There must be at least one attribute.

== Usage
./script/generate refinery singular_name attribute:type [attribute2:type ...]

== Examples
./script/generate refinery team_member title:string description:text
./script/generate refinery team_member title:string
./script/generate refinery team_member title:string description:text image:image

